## **3. openapi.yaml** (na raiz)
```yaml
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: SOCD Webhooks
  version: 1.0.0
paths:
  /webhook/health:
    get:
      summary: Health check
      responses:
        '200':
          description: OK
  /webhook/catalog/product:
    post:
      summary: Recebe webhook de produto
      responses:
        '200':
          description: OK
 
